### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:3333/user

### Get User by ID (replace 1 with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:3333/user/1

### Update User (replace 1 with actual user ID)
PUT http://localhost:3333/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updatedUsername",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

### Change User Role (Admin only - replace 1 with actual user ID)
PATCH http://localhost:3333/user/1/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "role": "ADMIN"
} 